item.title: Prayer bpn4928 in Vanuatu
item.description: O Yu we mi lavem fes blong Yu tumas, Yu we naesfala lukluk blong Yu i olsem wan ples we mi save stap sef long hem, Yu we ples blong Yu i gol blong mi, Yu we preis blong Yu i hop blong mi, Yu we kea blong Yu i stap wetem mi oltaem, Yu we lav blong Yu i mekem se mi stap long wol ia, Yu we taem mi tingbaot Yu mi harem gud tumas, Yu we mi wantem tumas blong mi stap klosap long Yu, Yu we mos impotan gol blong mi i blong stap long fored blong Yu!
